graph TD
    %% Interfaccia Utente
    Operator([Operator]) -->|Interacts| Frontend(mars-frontend)
    Frontend -->|HTTP/REST| Gateway(mars_api_gateway)

    %% Gateway e Gestione Dati
    Gateway -->|Routing| DBManager(mars_db_manager)
    Gateway -->|Routing| MemCache(mars_memory_cache)
    
    %% Storage Persistente e Volatile
    DBManager -->|Create/Delete Rules| Postgres[(postgres)]
    MemCache -->|Real Time Status| Redis[(redis)]

    %% Flusso Ingestione Dati
    Simulator(mars-simulator) -->|Raw Sensor Data| Ingestion(mars-ingestion-service)
    Ingestion -->|Event Normalization| Kafka{kafka}
    Zookeeper(zookeeper) -.-|Coordinates| Kafka

    %% Engine di Automazione (Core)
    Kafka -->|Consume Events| Consumer(mars_message_consumer)
    Consumer -->|Rule Check| DBManager
    Consumer -->|Update Status| MemCache
    Consumer -->|Trigger Actuators| Gateway